snippet.title: Osmozys - Atari Jaguar
snippet.description:
Osmozys for the Atari Jaguar is a demo created for the JagCode II competition.
The JagCode has turned into an annual activity and we hope more people will get interested in coding for the Jag... especially since there's prize money ;)
Anyway, this is one of the 3 entries.
It's a sequel to a previously-released game called DiamJag. It's a pretty fun game (the original) and I hope Osmozys will turn into a full-blown version :D
